unspliced = pre_TPM.T

# ---------- AnnData ----------
adata = sc.AnnData(X=spliced)
adata.layers["spliced"] = np.log1p(spliced.values)
adata.layers["unspliced"] = np.log1p(unspliced.values)
adata.obs_names = spliced.index
adata.var_names = spliced.columns

# metadata
